'''多窪馬鞍菌'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|en|'''Helvella lacunosa'''}}），俗稱'''石板灰鞍'''（{{lang|en|'''slate grey saddle'''}}）或'''凹槽黑色矮林鞍'''（{{lang|en|fluted black elfin saddle}}），是一種[[馬鞍菌屬|馬鞍菌屬]][[真菌|真菌]]，並且是目前最常見的馬鞍菌屬品種。<ref name=T.Laessoe>{{cite book | author = Thomas Laessoe | year = 1998 | title = Mushrooms (flexi bound) | publisher = Dorling Kindersley | isbn = 0-7513-1070-0}}</ref>這種真菌有著易於識別的不規則形狀灰色[[菌蓋|菌蓋]]、有凹槽的[[菌柄|菌柄]]和模糊的底面。這種真菌通常會於夏季和秋季在中國、日本、北美東部和歐洲的[[松柏門|松柏]]和[[落葉植物|落葉植物]]下出現。

==分類==
這種真菌最早是由博物學家[[亚当·阿夫塞柳斯|亚当·阿夫塞柳斯]]在1783年描述的。其[[植物學名命名法|學名]]源自拉丁文形容詞「lacunosa」，意思是「有洞的」。<ref name="Nilper77">Nilsson S, Persson O.(1977) ''Fungi of Northern Europe 1: Larger Fungi (Excluding Gill Fungi)''. pp. 36–37. Penguin Books. ISBN 0-14-063005-8</ref>蘇卡達馬鞍菌曾經被視為另一種真菌，但現在則因結構差異不大而被視為多窪馬鞍菌。<ref name = "MarcelBon87">{{cite book | author = Marcel Bon | year = 1987 | title = The Mushrooms and Toadstools of Britain and North Western Europe | url = https://archive.org/details/mushroomstoadsto0000bonm | publisher = Hodder and Stoughton | isbn = 0-340-39935-X}}</ref>

==描述==
[[File:Helvella_lacunosa_Karlštejn.jpg|thumb]]

多窪馬鞍菌有一個不規則的，折疊或起皺的菌蓋，其顏色為深淺不一的黑色或石板灰色，直徑為1–10&厘米（½–4英寸），但大部份為2–5厘米（1–2英寸）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mushroomexpert.com/helvella_lacunosa.html |title=Helvella lacunosa - MushroomExpert |access-date=2013-11-09 |archive-date=2021-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210219071804/http://www.mushroomexpert.com/helvella_lacunosa.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>其起皺的無環菌柄高3–15厘米（1–6英寸），早期呈白色，但隨著年齡增加會慢慢變暗，最終變成灰色。其[[孢子印|孢子印]]為白色，而橢圓形的擔孢子的大小則約為12 x 9微米。<ref name="arora86">{{cite book |last=Arora |first=David|authorlink=David Arora |year=1986 |title=Mushrooms demystified: a comprehensive guide to the fleshy fungi |url=https://archive.org/details/mushroomsdemysti00aror_0 |edition=2nd |location=Berkeley |publisher=Ten Speed Press |isbn=0-89815-169-4| pages=[https://archive.org/details/mushroomsdemysti00aror_0/page/815 815]–16}}</ref>有時候，白蓋多窪馬鞍菌亦會出現，並且可能與{{link-en|皱马鞍菌|Helvella crispa}}混淆。<ref name=Ammir85/>

==分佈及生境==
這種真菌於北美東部、歐洲<ref name="arora86"/>、日本<ref>{{cite journal |last= Nagao H.|year=2002 |title=Fungal flora in Chiba Pref., central Japan (III) Ascomycetes: Plectomycetes and Discomycetes |journal=Journal of the Natural History Museum and Institute Chiba  |volume=5 |issue= |pages=111–32|language=ja}}</ref>和中國非常常見。<ref>{{cite journal |last= Zhuang WY. |year=2004|title=Preliminary survey of the Helvellaceae from Xinjiang, China |journal=Mycotaxon |volume=90 |issue=1 |pages=35–42}}</ref>[[高山气候|高山气候]]和[[温带|温带]]都適合這種真菌生存<ref name=T.Laessoe/>，並且經常在[[松屬|松樹]]、[[栎属|橡樹]]和[[花旗松|花旗松]]附近出現。<ref name="arora86"/>子實體在夏末和秋季出現，但在加利福尼亞州有冬天出現子實體的記錄。<ref name="arora86"/>它們常在燒焦的地面處出現。<ref name = "Phillips06">{{cite book | author = Phillips R | year = 2006 | title = Mushrooms |page= 360| publisher = Pan Macmillan Ltd|location=London| isbn=0-330-44237-6}}</ref>

一些標本有著白色的發霉外觀，全因它們被[[菌寄生屬|菌寄生屬]]真菌寄生。<ref name="arora86"/><ref name="Nguyen 2013">{{cite journal |author=Nguyen NH, Landeros F, Garibay-Orijel R, Hansen K, Vellinga EC. |title=The ''Helvella lacunosa'' species complex in western North America: Cryptic species, misapplied names and parasites |journal=Mycologia |year=2013 |volume=105 |issue=5 |pages=1275–86 |doi=10.3852/12-391 |pmid=23709487}}</ref>

==可食性==
這種真菌經烹調後是一種知名的食物，但其菌柄則不供食用。<ref name="arora86"/>幾本旅遊指南均列出了這種真菌可供食用<ref name = "Phillips06"/><ref name=Haas69>{{cite book | last = Haas |first=Hans | year = 1969 | title = The Young Specialist looks at Fungi |page= 184| publisher = Burke | isbn= 0-222-79409-7}}</ref>，但這種真菌現在被懷疑擁有有毒化合物，並且曾有人們生吃後引起胃腸道症狀的案例。<ref name=Ammir85>{{cite book |last=Ammirati |first=Joseph F.|coauthors= James A Traquair and Paul A Horgen |title=Poisonous mushrooms of the northern United States and Canada |url=https://archive.org/details/poisonousmushroo00amma |year=1985 |publisher=University of Minnesota Press |location=Minneapolis |isbn=0-8166-1407-5 |page=[https://archive.org/details/poisonousmushroo00amma/page/259 259]}}</ref>

